{"tid":1960650,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"我是BNO。今次秘魯能成功回港，感謝英國政府。","createTime":"2020-04-06T09:33:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T18:12:41.000Z","uid":79563,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c3b8885370cb638fb774e4a9eb2a14a66e666950","tid":1960650,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T09:33:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4254264/org/a97f48f70dd04e591a938aeaaf8ceafb.jpg/UZ2oiajo8FXUcrGus99mgj_ctn8r7HxYS_6y6Uv-suk?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4254264%2Forg%2Fa97f48f70dd04e591a938aeaaf8ceafb.jpg%2FUZ2oiajo8FXUcrGus99mgj_ctn8r7HxYS_6y6Uv-suk%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=e86befc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我是BNO。<br />\n<br />\n今次秘魯能成功回港，感謝英國政府。<br />\n<br />\n本人同太太去秘魯旅行，不幸遇上武漢肺炎，四周一片混亂。雖然我們趕上機場，不幸我們所乘坐的中國航空取消了航班。<br />\n<br />\n我們感到傍徨無助，因為身上乾糧不多，可能斷水斷糧。<br />\n<br />\n一個小時後，手機竟收到英國大使館短訊，所有英國國民，包括BNO，可在候機大堂集合，英國政府已派專機接走國民。<br />\n<br />\n五個小時後我已成功登上英國航空，上機時只作了登記，到現在還未收我機票錢，我地是第一批離開利馬的人。<br />\n<br />\n我知道其他國家包括支那及香港遊客都走不了，因為利馬機場得一條跑道，優先給了英國航空、維珍航空等<br />\n<br />\n此時此刻特別想說，作為英國人，就算是爛船都有三斤釘的BNO也好，特別特別的幸福！<br />\n<br />\n在此希望滞溜在秘魯遊客大家平安，順利撤出。<br />\n<br />\nDanny<br />\n31/3/2020<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://whatsnew2day.b-cdn.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Passengers-burst-into-applause-when-British-Airways-repatriation-flight-from.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwhatsnew2day.b-cdn.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2FPassengers-burst-into-applause-when-British-Airways-repatriation-flight-from.jpg&h=c3b7184f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">[以上是支那潮文改編, 純粹虛構。]</span></strong>"},{"pid":"4d60d6980ceb727b4045948bacced556f80ac460","tid":1960650,"uid":41087,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T09:42:15.000Z","msg":"3m 6800<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99de1231e9e9d274f02ffd781da121ecf2e3460a","tid":1960650,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T09:44:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d23db506e71c10690cbc9a1daff2c7178a80abb","tid":1960650,"uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"4d60d6980ceb727b4045948bacced556f80ac460","tid":1960650,"uid":41087,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T09:42:15.000Z","msg":"3m 6800<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T09:48:56.000Z","msg":"有BNO, 又有3m 6800<br />\n<br />\n可能係手足嚟"},{"pid":"8588e826b1d005e8362c42101552c8cc7d5b8184","tid":1960650,"uid":146797,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T10:59:03.000Z","msg":"支持bno，hkip不了"},{"pid":"d672406089fe6b0ac992cbd26a528b6a5d14176a","tid":1960650,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8588e826b1d005e8362c42101552c8cc7d5b8184","tid":1960650,"uid":146797,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T10:59:03.000Z","msg":"支持bno，hkip不了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T04:36:12.000Z","msg":"hkip好似係城邦太子搞, 好驚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b63c2352534fb292ec889906b08b235f26683a65","tid":1960650,"uid":265980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3b8885370cb638fb774e4a9eb2a14a66e666950","tid":1960650,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T09:33:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4254264/org/a97f48f70dd04e591a938aeaaf8ceafb.jpg/UZ2oiajo8FXUcrGus99mgj_ctn8r7HxYS_6y6Uv-suk?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4254264%2Forg%2Fa97f48f70dd04e591a938aeaaf8ceafb.jpg%2FUZ2oiajo8FXUcrGus99mgj_ctn8r7HxYS_6y6Uv-suk%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=e86befc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我是BNO。<br />\n<br />\n今次